M||titl|Cache Repeated fn Calls
M||impa|md
M||impa|avoid redundant computation
M||tags|javascript, cache, memoization, perf
M||tx|---
M|Cach|tx|Use a md-level Map to cache fn results when the same fn is called repeatedly w/ the same inputs during render.
M|Cach|**In|**
M|Cach|tx|```ts
M|Cach|func|{ projects: Project[] }) {
M|Cach|tx|return (
M|Cach|tx|<div>
M|Cach|tx|{projects.map(project => {
M|Cach|tx|// slugify() called 100+ times for same project names
M|Cach|tx|const slug = slugify(project.name)
M|Cach|tx|return <ProjectCard key={project.id} slug={slug} />
M|Cach|tx|})}
M|Cach|tx|</div>
M|Cach|tx|)
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|```
M|Cach|**Co|**
M|Cach|tx|```ts
M|Cach|tx|// md-level cache
M|Cach|tx|const slugifyCache = new Map<string, string>()
M|Cach|func|string): string {
M|Cach|tx|if (slugifyCache.has(text)) {
M|Cach|tx|return slugifyCache.get(text)!
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|const result = slugify(text)
M|Cach|tx|slugifyCache.set(text, result)
M|Cach|tx|return result
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|func|{ projects: Project[] }) {
M|Cach|tx|return (
M|Cach|tx|<div>
M|Cach|tx|{projects.map(project => {
M|Cach|tx|// Computed only once per unique project name
M|Cach|tx|const slug = cachedSlugify(project.name)
M|Cach|tx|return <ProjectCard key={project.id} slug={slug} />
M|Cach|tx|})}
M|Cach|tx|</div>
M|Cach|tx|)
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|```
M|Cach|**Si|**
M|Cach|tx|```ts
M|Cach|let |boolean \| null = null
M|Cach|func|boolean {
M|Cach|tx|if (isLoggedInCache !== null) {
M|Cach|tx|return isLoggedInCache
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|isLoggedInCache = document.cookie.includes('auth=')
M|Cach|tx|return isLoggedInCache
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|// Clear cache when auth changes
M|Cach|tx|fn onAuthChange() {
M|Cach|tx|isLoggedInCache = null
M|Cach|tx|}
M|Cach|tx|```
M|Cach|Use |utilities, event handlers, not just rc cp.
